OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772655072
OL,3,CCan Wolves pull off the greatest
OL,4,Cescape in Premier League history?
OL,6,FThey couldn't, could they?
OL,7,FWolverhampton Wanderers were destined
OL,8,Ffor Premier League relegation but
OL,9,Funlikely wins against Aston Villa and
OL,10,FLiverpool has some in Molineux
OL,11,Fdreaming.
OL,13,FWolves are now just three points
OL,14,Fbehind second bottom Burnley.
OL,15,FSomething that was unthinkable just a
OL,16,Fcouple of weeks ago.
OL,18,FUntil last night, most Wolves fans
OL,19,Fwould find looking at the table a
OL,20,Fpointless exercise.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
