OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772655072
OL,3,CCan Wolves pull off the greatest
OL,4,Cescape in Premier League history?
OL,6,FI'd be surprised if Wolves finish
OL,7,Fbottom but they've surely left
OL,8,Fthemselves too much to do to survive?
OL,9,FNottingham Forest are fourth bottom.
OL,10,FThey are 11 points clear of Wolves
OL,11,Fwith two games in hand.
OL,13,FRob Edwards appointed as new
OL,14,FWolverhampton Wanderers head coach
OL,16,FWith eight games to go, Wolves can
OL,17,Fonly collect another 24 points so they
OL,18,Fare more like cats on life number nine.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
